Requirements
============

(with root user)

	Debian like (Debian, Ubuntu ...)
	--------------------------------

		apt-get update
		apt-get install sudo uuid-runtime curl xvfb bzip2 libbz2-dev

	Ubuntu
	------

		apt-get update
		apt-get install libevent-dev libxrender1 libfontconfig1

Environment
===========

(with root user)

		useradd -m -d /opt/canopsis -s /bin/bash canopsis

Installation
============

		mv canopsis_installer /opt/canopsis
		su - canopsis
		cd canopsis_installer
		./install.sh

And now, logout and re-login.
